 "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31662100/31662025/88857f6e_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31662100/31662025/9991aa1b_z.jpg"}}}], "descriptions": {"headline": "With a stay at 4 Rivers Hotel in Phnom Penh (Daun Penh), you'll be steps from Riverside and 3 minutes by foot from Royal Palace.  This hotel is 0.5 mi (0.9 km) from National Museum of Cambodia and 0.5 mi (0.9 km) from Silver Pagoda.\n\nEnjoy a meal at 4 Rivers, or stay in and take advantage of the hotel's 24-hour room service. Wrap up your day with a drink at the bar/lounge.\n\nPamper yourself with onsite massages or take in the view from a terrace. Additional amenities at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access and concierge services.\n\nMake yourself at home in one of the 13 air-conditioned rooms featuring minibars. Complimentary wireless internet access is available to keep you connected. Bathrooms have deep soaking bathtubs and complimentary toiletries. Conveniences include phones, as well as desks and electric kettles.", "default": "{\"amenities\":\"Pamper yourself with onsite massages or take in the view from a terrace. Additional amenities at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access and concierge services.\",\"spoken_languages\":\"Khmer, Vietnamese, Thai, English, French\",\"rooms\":\"Make yourself at home in one of the 13 air-conditioned rooms featuring minibars. Complimentary wireless internet access is available to keep you connected. Bathrooms have deep soaking bathtubs and complimentary toiletries. Conveniences include phones, as well as desks and electric kettles.\",\"onsite_payments\":\"Visa, Debit cards, Cash, JCB International, Mastercard, UnionPay\",\"dining\":\"Enjoy a meal at 4 Rivers, or stay in and take advantage of the hotel's 24-hour room service. Wrap up your day with a drink at the bar/lounge.\",\"business_amenities\":\"Featured amenities include a business center, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Free self parking is available onsite.\",\"location\":\"With a stay at 4 Rivers Hotel in Phnom Penh (Daun Penh), you'll be steps from Riverside and 3 minutes by foot from Royal Palace.  This hotel is 0.5 mi (0.9 km) from National Museum of Cambodia and 0.5 mi (0.9 km) from Silver Pagoda.\",\"attractions\":\"Distances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer.  Riverside - 0.1 km / 0.1 mi  Royal Palace Park - 0.1 km / 0.1 mi  Royal Palace - 0.2 km / 0.1 mi  313 Quayside - 0.3 km / 0.2 mi  Wat Ounalom - 0.3 km / 0.2 mi  Riverfront Park - 0.4 km / 0.2 mi  National Museum of Cambodia - 0.4 km / 0.3 mi  Kandal Market - 0.6 km / 0.4 mi  Chaktomouk Conference Hall - 0.6 km / 0.4 mi  Silver Pagoda - 0.9 km / 0.5 mi  Cambodia-Vietnam Friendship Monument - 1 km / 0.6 mi  Phnom Penh Night Market - 1.1 km / 0.7 mi  Old Market - 1.1 km / 0.7 mi  Wat Botum - 1.1 km / 0.7 mi  Sosoro Museum - 1.4 km / 0.8 mi  The nearest major airport is Phnom Penh Intl. Airport (PNH) - 11.5 km / 7.1 mi\",\"headline\":\"Near Royal Palace\"}"}, "rooms": {"0": {"id": "0", "room_inventory": "Run of House"}}, "status": {"success": true, "httpStatus": 200}}}
