riginal": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/22218940_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/f28fa318_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/1ef0d612_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/b8c3e827_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/e14ae59b_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/fef9c4c9_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/a55b4e4c_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/1f05ca4a_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/7b618576_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/a49e84f5_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/d119b329_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/a1b00907_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/1000000/30000/20200/20189/995a1c6f_z.jpg"}}}], "descriptions": {"headline": "President, Mumbai - IHCL SeleQtions is centrally located in Mumbai, a 3-minute walk from Colaba Causeway and 7 minutes by foot from World Trade Centre.  This luxury hotel is 1 mi (1.7 km) from Afghan Church and 1.2 mi (1.9 km) from Maharashtra State Assembly.\n\nEnjoy Italian cuisine at Trattoria, one of the hotel's 3 restaurants, or stay in and take advantage of the 24-hour room service. Snacks are also available at the coffee shop/cafe. Mingle with other guests at the complimentary reception, held daily. Quench your thirst with your favorite drink at the bar/lounge. Buffet breakfasts are available daily from 7 AM to 10 AM for a fee.\n\nRelax at the full-service spa, where you can enjoy massages, body treatments, and facials. You can take advantage of recreational amenities such as an outdoor pool, a sauna, and a fitness center. Additional features at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and gift shops/newsstands.\n\nMake yourself at home in one of the 287 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and DVD players. 32-inch LCD televisions with cable programming provide entertainment, while complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected. Private bathrooms with showers feature rainfall showerheads and complimentary toiletries. Conveniences include phones, as well as laptop-compatible safes and desks.", "default": "{\"amenities\":\"Relax at the full-service spa, where you can enjoy massages, body treatments, and facials. You can take advantage of recreational amenities such as an outdoor pool, a sauna, and a fitness center. Additional features at this hotel include complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and gift shops/newsstands.\",\"spoken_languages\":\"Hindi, English\",\"rooms\":\"Make yourself at home in one of the 287 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and DVD players. 32-inch LCD televisions with cable programming provide entertainment, while complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected. Private bathrooms with showers feature rainfall showerheads and complimentary toiletries. Conveniences include phones, as well as laptop-compatible safes and desks.\",\"onsite_payments\":\"Visa, Diners Club, Debit cards, Cash, American Express, Mastercard\",\"dining\":\"Enjoy Italian cuisine at Trattoria, one of the hotel's 3 restaurants, or stay in and take advantage of the 24-hour room service. Snacks are also available at the coffee shop/cafe. Mingle with other guests at the complimentary reception, held daily. Quench your thirst with your favorite drink at the bar/lounge. Buffet breakfasts are available daily from 7 AM to 10 AM for a fee.\",\"business_amenities\":\"Featured amenities include a 24-hour business center, limo/town car service, and express check-in. Planning an event in Mumbai? This hotel has 12917 square feet (1200 square meters) of space consisting of conference space and 4 meeting rooms. A roundtrip airport shuttle is provided for a surcharge (available 24 hours), and free self parking is available onsite.\",\"location\":\"President, Mumbai - IHCL SeleQtions is centrally located in Mumbai, a 3-minute walk from Colaba Causeway and 7 minutes by foot from World Trade Centre.  This luxury hotel is 1 mi (1.7 km) from Afghan Church and 1.2 mi (1.9 km) from Maharashtra State Assembly.\",\"attractions\":\"Distances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer.  Colaba Causeway - 0.3 km / 0.2 mi  Mumbai Port Trust Garden - 0.5 km / 0.3 mi  World Trade Centre - 0.6 km / 0.4 mi  Front Bay - 1.3 km / 0.8 mi  Maharashtra State Lawn Tennis Association - 1.3 km / 0.8 mi  Afghan Church - 1.5 km / 0.9 mi  Cooperage Ground - 1.5 km / 0.9 mi  Mantralaya - 1.7 km / 1.1 mi  Maharashtra State Assembly - 1.8 km / 1.1 mi  MCGM Garden Oshiwara - 1.9 km / 1.2 mi  Jehangir Art Gallery - 2.1 km / 1.3 mi  Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Museum - 2.1 km / 1.3 mi  Rajabai Tower - 2.2 km / 1.3 mi  Air India Building - 2.3 km / 1.4 mi  Bombay High Court - 2.3 km / 1.4 mi  The nearest airports are:Chhatrapati Shivaji International Airport (BOM) - 29.4 km / 18.3 mi Navi Mumbai Intl. Airport (NMI) - 41.1 km / 25.5 mi The preferred airport for President, Mumbai - IHCL SeleQtions is Chhatrapati Shivaji International Airport (BOM). \",\"headline\":\"In Mumbai (Colaba)\"}"}, "rooms": {"44": {"id": "10024552295", "room_count": 1, "room_inventory": "Superior", "bed_config": {"bed_count": 1, "bedroom_count": 1, "configuration": {"0": {"quantity": 1}}}, "occupancy": {"max_allowed": {"total": 0, "adults": 0, "children": 0}}}, "45": {"id": "10024506910", "room_count": 1, "room_inventory": "Superior", "bed_config": {"bed_count": 1, "bedroom_count": 1, "configuration": {"0": {"quantity": 1}}}, "occupancy": {"max_allowed": {"total": 0, "adults": 0, "children": 0}}}, "46": {"id": "10024506877", "room_count": 1, "room_inventory": "Executive Suite", "amenities": {"44": {"id": "6176", "name": "Non-Smoking"}, "45": {"id": "26", "name": "Television"}, "46": {"id": "2056", "name": "Turndown service"}, "47": {"id": "2034", "name": "Premium bedding"}, "48": {"id": "1073743289", "name": "Electric kettle"}, "49": {"id": "2572", "name": "Pillow menu"}, "50": {"id": "1073744237", "name": "Laptop-friendly workspace"}, "51": {"id": "2151", "name": "In-room childcare (surcharge)"}, "52": {"id": "2150", "name": "Blackout drapes/curtains"}, "53": {"id": "130", "name": "Refrigerator"}, "10": {"id": "133", "name": "Daily housekeeping"}, "54": {"id": "133", "name": "Daily housekeeping"}, "11": {"id": "2403", "name": "Free WiFi"}, "55": {"id": "2403", "name": "Free WiFi"}, "12": {"id": "2402", "name": "HDTV"}, "56": {"id": "2402", "name": "HDTV"}, "13": {"id": "135", "name": "Hypo-allergenic bedding available"}, "57": {"id": "135", "name": "Hypo-allergenic bedding available"}, "14": {"id": "136", "name": "Phone"}, "58": {"id": "136", "name": "Phone"}, "15": {"id": "2389", "name": "In-room safe (laptop compatible)"}, "59": {"id": "2389", "name": "In-room safe (laptop compatible)"}, "16": {"id": "2026", "name": "Desk"}, "17": {"id": "1073743370", "name": "Towels provided"}, "18": {"id": "2081", "name": "Premium TV channels"}, "19": {"id": "1073743371", "name": "Bedsheets provided"}, "0": {"id": 