 a health declaration.,Mandatory fees: Guests booked in Breakfast Included rate plans are charged an additional VAT at check-in or check-out.,Optional fees:  - Fee for buffet breakfast: approximately INR 850 per person\n- Airport shuttle fee: INR 4250 per vehicle (one-way, maximum occupancy 4)\n- Pet deposit: INR 3500 per stay\n- Pet fee: INR 3000 per pet, per day\n- Early check-in is available for a fee (subject to availability)\n- Rollaway bed fee: INR 3000.0 per night\n The above list may not be comprehensive. Fees and deposits may not include tax and are subject to change. \n,Know before you go:    - One child 11 years old or younger stays free when occupying the parent or guardian's room, using existing bedding. \n- Only registered guests are allowed in the guestrooms. \n - Free in-room WiFi has a 4-device limit. WiFi in public areas is also free and has a 4-device limit. \n- Contactless check-in and contactless check-out are available.\n- At check-in, guests must provide a record of full COVID-19 vaccination.\n- Guests providing vaccine records must have received complete COVID-19 vaccination at least 3 days prior to check-in.\n ,Tax Recovery Charges and Service Fees for 2 people: 90.54 USD (This amount is included within the total price).,Tax Recovery Charges and Service Fees for 2 people: 89.55 USD (This amount is included within the total price).,Tax Recovery Charges and Service Fees for 2 people: 116.14 USD (This amount is included within the total price).\nPromotion: Non-refundable rate. No amendments permitted NON-REFUNDABLE RATE\nIncludes accommodation and free WiFi for four devices. Additional taxes applicable.-.\nIncludes buffet breakfast and WiFi with a flexible cancellation policy.  \nChildren accompanying guests who book meal inclusive plans will be entitled to a free stay in the existing bedding on room only basis. For meal inclusion, a child supplement would be charged at the designated outlet. Applicable taxes are extra.-.\nRate Includes Breakfa