e": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31663700/31663606/cc8e81db_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31663700/31663606/bd314438_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31663700/31663606/f6923d91_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31663700/31663606/f17d4c34_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31663700/31663606/8cfd293d_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31663700/31663606/4e006815_z.jpg"}}}], "descriptions": {"headline": "With a stay at Landgasthof Alte Bergm\u00fchle in Dreieich, you'll be 10 mi (16 km) from MyZeil and 10.2 mi (16.4 km) from Frankfurt Christmas Market.  This hotel is 10.2 mi (16.4 km) from R\u00f6merberg and 10.7 mi (17.2 km) from Alte Oper.\n\nEnjoy a satisfying meal at Alte Bergm\u00fchle serving guests of Landgasthof Alte Bergm\u00fchle. Buffet breakfasts are available daily from 7:00 AM to 11:00 AM for a fee.\n\nStay in one of 14 guestrooms featuring flat-screen televisions. Satellite television is provided for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with bathtubs or showers feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include desks, housekeeping is provided daily, and cribs/infant beds (complimentary) can be requested.", "default": "{\"spoken_languages\":\"German\",\"rooms\":\"Stay in one of 14 guestrooms featuring flat-screen televisions. Satellite television is provided for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with bathtubs or showers feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include desks, housekeeping is provided daily, and cribs/infant beds (complimentary) can be requested.\",\"renovations\":\"The following facilities are closed on Monday and Sunday: Dining venue(s)\",\"onsite_payments\":\"Visa, Debit cards not accepted, Cash not accepted, American Express, Mastercard\",\"dining\":\"Enjoy a satisfying meal at Alte Bergm\u00fchle serving guests of Landgasthof Alte Bergm\u00fchle. Buffet breakfasts are available daily from 7:00 AM to 11:00 AM for a fee.\",\"business_amenities\":\"Free self parking is available onsite.\",\"location\":\"With a stay at Landgasthof Alte Bergm\u00fchle in Dreieich, you'll be 10 mi (16 km) from MyZeil and 10.2 mi (16.4 km) from Frankfurt Christmas Market.  This hotel is 10.2 mi (16.4 km) from R\u00f6merberg and 10.7 mi (17.2 km) from Alte Oper.\",\"attractions\":\"Distances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer.  Langener Waldsee - 11.9 km / 7.4 mi  Messel Pit Fossil Site - 12 km / 7.5 mi  Henninger Turm - 14.1 km / 8.8 mi  Bergstrasse-Odenwald Nature Park - 14.3 km / 8.9 mi  Museumsufer - 14.8 km / 9.2 mi  Capitol - 15 km / 9.3 mi  German Leather Museum - 15.1 km / 9.4 mi  Messe Offenbach - 15.2 km / 9.4 mi  Buesing Palais - 15.4 km / 9.5 mi  Isenburg Palace - 15.4 km / 9.6 mi  Schirn Art Museum - 15.4 km / 9.6 mi  Frankfurt Cathedral - 15.4 km / 9.6 mi  Frankfurt Historical Museum - 15.4 km / 9.6 mi  German Film Museum - 15.7 km / 9.7 mi  German Architecture Museum - 15.7 km / 9.7 mi  The nearest airports are:Frankfurt Airport (FRA) - 21.9 km / 13.6 mi Mainz (QFZ-Mainz Finthen) - 59.6 km / 37 mi Frankfurt (HHN-Frankfurt - Hahn) - 134.1 km / 83.3 mi \",\"headline\":\"In Dreieich\"}"}, "rooms": {"0": {"id": "0", "room_inventory": "Run of House"}}, "status": {"success": true, "httpStatus": 200}}}
