ginal": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31664500/31664409/ec10a118_z.jpg"}}}, {"is_hero_image": false, "links": {"original": {"href": "https://i.travelapi.com/lodging/32000000/31670000/31664500/31664409/e5e55327_z.jpg"}}}], "descriptions": {"headline": "Romeo Giulietta Rooms Apartments Turkish Bath is centrally located in Verona, a 4-minute walk from Giardino Giusti and 10 minutes by foot from Juliet's House.  This bed & breakfast is 0.9 mi (1.5 km) from University of Verona and 1.1 mi (1.7 km) from Piazza delle Erbe.\n\nContinental breakfasts are available daily from 7:30 AM to 12:30 PM for a fee.\n\nTake advantage of recreation opportunities such as bicycles to rent or take in the view from a terrace and a garden. This bed & breakfast also features complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and bicycle tour information.\n\nMake yourself at home in one of the 5 guestrooms. Your room comes with a memory foam bed. Rooms have private furnished balconies or patios. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with showers feature rainfall showerheads and complimentary toiletries.", "default": "{\"amenities\":\"Take advantage of recreation opportunities such as bicycles to rent or take in the view from a terrace and a garden. This bed & breakfast also features complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and bicycle tour information.\",\"spoken_languages\":\"German, English, Italian\",\"rooms\":\"Make yourself at home in one of the 5 guestrooms. Your room comes with a memory foam bed. Rooms have private furnished balconies or patios. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with showers feature rainfall showerheads and complimentary toiletries.\",\"onsite_payments\":\"Carte Blanche, Visa, Debit cards not accepted, Cash, American Express, JCB International, Mastercard\",\"dining\":\"Continental breakfasts are available daily from 7:30 AM to 12:30 PM for a fee.\",\"business_amenities\":\"Featured amenities include a 24-hour front desk, luggage storage, and laundry facilities. A shuttle from the airport to the hotel is provided for a surcharge (available 24 hours), and self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite.\",\"location\":\"Romeo Giulietta Rooms Apartments Turkish Bath is centrally located in Verona, a 4-minute walk from Giardino Giusti and 10 minutes by foot from Juliet's House.  This bed & breakfast is 0.9 mi (1.5 km) from University of Verona and 1.1 mi (1.7 km) from Piazza delle Erbe.\",\"attractions\":\"Distances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer.  Giardino Giusti - 0.3 km / 0.2 mi  Verona Archeological Museum - 0.4 km / 0.3 mi  SS. Siro e Libera - 0.4 km / 0.3 mi  San Tomaso Cantuariense - 0.5 km / 0.3 mi  Roman Theater - 0.6 km / 0.4 mi  Adige River - 0.6 km / 0.4 mi  Ponte Pietra - 0.7 km / 0.4 mi  Juliet's House - 0.8 km / 0.5 mi  St. Peter's Castle - 0.9 km / 0.6 mi  Palazzo Forti - 1 km / 0.6 mi  San Fermo Maggiore - 1 km / 0.6 mi  University of Verona - 1 km / 0.6 mi  Chiesa di San Pietro Martire - 1 km / 0.6 mi  Chiesa di San Fermo - 1 km / 0.6 mi  Sant'Anastasia - 1 km / 0.6 mi  The preferred airport for Romeo Giulietta Rooms Apartments Turkish Bath is Valerio Catullo Airport (VRN) - 15 km / 9.3 mi \",\"headline\":\"Near Juliet's House\"}"}, "rooms": {"0": {"id": "0", "room_inventory": "Run of House"}}, "status": {"success": true, "httpStatus": 200}}}
